graph LR
    ModelRegistryOp[Model Registry Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    ModelRegistryOp -->|metadata storage| PostgreSQL[PostgreSQL 16+<br/>postgresql-16-c10s]
    ModelRegistryOp -->|alternative DB| MySQL[MySQL 3306+]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    ModelRegistryOp -.->|auth proxy| KubeRBACProxy[kube-rbac-proxy<br/>latest]
    ModelRegistryOp -.->|TLS certs| CertManager[cert-manager]
    ModelRegistryOp -.->|auto TLS| ServiceCA[OpenShift Service CA]
    ModelRegistryOp -.->|service mesh| Istio[Istio/Service Mesh]

    %% Core Kubernetes
    ModelRegistryOp -->|CR reconciliation| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]
    ModelRegistryOp -->|ingress| OpenShiftRouter[OpenShift Router]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    ModelRegistryOp -->|CRD watch| PlatformComponents[components.platform<br/>.opendatahub.io]
    ModelRegistryOp -->|auth config| PlatformServices[services.platform<br/>.opendatahub.io<br/>auths]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -.->|UI management| ModelRegistryOp
    DSPipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|model logging| ModelRegistryInstance[Model Registry Instance]
    KServe[KServe] -.->|model metadata| ModelRegistryInstance

    %% Managed Instance
    ModelRegistryOp -->|creates/manages| ModelRegistryInstance
    ModelRegistryInstance -->|persists to| PostgreSQL
    ModelRegistryInstance -->|persists to| MySQL

    %% Optional Features
    ModelRegistryOp -.->|optional| ModelCatalog[Model Catalog<br/>curated metadata]

